window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>From </b><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> and Audible best-selling author Ben H. Winters comes a twisty tale of time travel and two women who must save each other–no matter the cost.</b></p> <p>Annie has always had high hopes for her future. But the reality of her life just isn’t measuring up. She loves her fiancé, Greg–doesn’t she? She’s going to get her degree and open her own business–won’t she?</p> <p>Then, a strange old woman shows up outside her house, and she seems to know a lot about Annie. An awful lot.</p> <p>Annie could tell the old woman to get lost. Yet there’s something about her Annie just can’t shake. And what she learns could change her life forever–but is it the life she envisioned?</p>"; 
